data <- read.csv("~/Investigacion/Data/Entropia/Pruebas sin tiempos/ImSim100x100_DosPar_Vent5_L3Gamma5SinLNniTiempos")
data <- data %>% select(n,alfa,gama,alfa.MV,gama.MV,HMV.est,HVE.est,
                        HNA.est,HC.est,AHE.est,media,varianza)
alfa_code <- factor(data$alfa, levels = c("-1.5","-3","-5","-8"),
                        ordered = TRUE, labels=1:4)
alfas.MV<-matrix(data$alfa.MV,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE)
alfas<-matrix(as.numeric(alfa_code),nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE)
par(mfrow=c(1,2))
image(alfas,col=gray.colors(4),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="alfa")
image(alfas.MV,col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="alfa MV")

Mapa de entropias

par(mfrow=c(2,3))
image(matrix(as.numeric(alfa_code),nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="alfa")
image(matrix(data$AHE.est,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="AHE.est")
image(matrix(data$HVE.est,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="HVE.est")
image(matrix(data$HNA.est,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="HNA.est")
image(matrix(data$HC.est,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="HC.est")
image(matrix(data$HMV.est,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray(1:1000/1000),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="HMV.est")

K medias

set.seed(123) 
input_kmeans1<-data %>% select(AHE.est)
km1 <- kmeans(x = input_kmeans1, centers = 4)
set.seed(123) 
input_kmeans2<-data %>% select(HC.est)
km2 <- kmeans(x = input_kmeans2, centers = 4)
set.seed(123) 
input_kmeans3<-data %>% select(HVE.est)
km3 <- kmeans(x = input_kmeans3, centers = 4)
set.seed(123) 
input_kmeans4<-data %>% select(HNA.est)
km4 <- kmeans(x = input_kmeans4, centers = 4)
set.seed(123) 
input_kmeans5<-data %>% select(HMV.est)
km5 <- kmeans(x = input_kmeans5, centers = 4)
par(mfrow=c(2,3))
image(matrix(as.numeric(alfa_code),nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="alfa")
image(matrix(km1$cluster,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = c(0,1,2,3,4),axes=F,main="HAHE")
image(matrix(km2$cluster,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = c(0,1,2,3,4),axes=F,main="HC")
image(matrix(km3$cluster,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HVE")
image(matrix(km4$cluster,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HNA")
image(matrix(km5$cluster,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HMV")

#Codifico las salidas de k means:

#- 1: (gris mas oscuro) corresponde a la clase -1.5
#- 2: corresponde a la clase -3
#- 3: corresponde a la clase -5
#- 4: (gris mas claro) corresponde a la clase -8

cluster1<-km1$cluster
cluster2<-km2$cluster
cluster3<-km3$cluster
cluster4<-km4$cluster
cluster5<-km5$cluster

cluster3[km3$cluster==1]<-2
cluster3[km3$cluster==2]<-1
cluster4[km4$cluster==1]<-2
cluster4[km4$cluster==2]<-1
cluster5[km5$cluster==1]<-2
cluster5[km5$cluster==2]<-1
par(mfrow=c(2,3))
image(matrix(as.numeric(alfa_code),nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1, axes=FALSE,main="alfa")
image(matrix(cluster1,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = c(0,1,2,3,4),axes=F,main="HAHE")
image(matrix(cluster2,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = c(0,1,2,3,4),axes=F,main="HC")
image(matrix(cluster3,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HVE")
image(matrix(cluster4,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HNA")
image(matrix(cluster5,nrow=96,ncol=96,byrow = TRUE),col=gray.colors(4),asp=1,breaks = 
c(0,1,2,3,4), axes=F,main="HMV")

cf1<-confusionMatrix(as.factor(cluster1),alfa_code)
cf2<-confusionMatrix(as.factor(cluster2),alfa_code)
cf3<-confusionMatrix(as.factor(cluster3),alfa_code)
cf4<-confusionMatrix(as.factor(cluster4),alfa_code)
cf5<-confusionMatrix(as.factor(cluster5),alfa_code)

acc.AHE<-cf1$overall[1]
acc.HC <-cf2$overall[1]
acc.HVE<-cf3$overall[1]
acc.HNA<-cf4$overall[1]
acc.HMV<-cf5$overall[1]
gamma5<-data.frame(AHE=acc.AHE,HC=acc.HC,HVE=acc.HVE,HNA=acc.HNA,HMV=acc.HMV)
gamma5
